						               													<description>Bang the Button!!! is an educational  and interactive game that has been developed for learners of English as a foreign language for beginner levels. (Starters, A1 and A2, according to the Common European Framework of Reference for Languages (CEFR)).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It is a unique, very complete game that can (and should) be used as a complement to any method (digital or more traditional) that is used in the classroom. Playing the game at home is of course also great fun!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Especially the oral skills (speaking and listening) are trained in this game that is played in small groups (3 &amp;ndash; 6 players). The game allows a lot of interaction between the players, exactly what we want in foreign language teaching.&amp;#10;The game is also very useful for getting rid of the usual shyness that many learners feel. The game is very challenging and educational.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game Bang the Button is, as mentioned above, very complete and includes a variety of aspects, such as:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     vocabulary&amp;#10;     grammar&amp;#10;     communication&amp;#10;     culture&amp;#10;     movement&amp;#10;     interaction&amp;#10;     constant participation of all players&amp;#10;     a healthy dose of competion&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
